Membership
Come for the Golf, Stay for the Friends!
Being a member of our private golf club in Sun City Center, FL allows you to enjoy golf at your pace in a supportive, friendly environment. Our open, inclusive golf groups and extensive social activities will draw you in…you’ll make many new friends after becoming a member.
Are you on the fence about joining a private golf course? Try us out for a 2 to 12 month trial membership to see if we fit for you!
Want to join in the fun at Caloosa and don’t play golf? Come join us for the social activities at Caloosa.

Membership Types:
General memberships for individuals and couples
Snowbird memberships for individuals and couples (October through May of the membership year)
International memberships for individuals and couples with non-USA residence. (Minimum 4 months membership required)
Limited term Trial memberships 2 to 12 months for individuals and couples
Social memberships for non-golfers
Membership benefits:
No monthly minimums
No trail fees
Unlimited golf
Unlimited range balls for members and guests
Unlimited use of practice facilities
Individual golf memberships include a social membership for spouse or partner
New
General Member (Annual Membership)
12 Month Membership: October 1, 2025 through September 30, 2026.
Join during October 1, 2025 through December 31, 2025 and play the remainder of 2025
FREE
We also have an option to join during June 1, 2025 through September 30, 2025. Pay the prorated dues for the remainder of the 2024-2025 season [that ends September 30, 2025] and you still qualify for the 2025-2026 season promotion mentioned above. Your payment must include the prorated 2024-2025 dues and the promotional 2025-2026 dues.
Annual price:  General Single: $3,882.79   General Couple: $5,584.19
Promotion Price:  General Single: $2,912.09   General Couple: $4,188.14
New
Snowbird Members (Annual Membership)
8 Month Membership: October 1, 2025 through May 31, 2026
Joint October 1, 2025 through November 30, 2025 and receive one month
FREE
Annual Price:  Snowbird Single: $3,246.51  Snowbird Couple: $4,681.86
October Promotion Price:  Snowbird Single: $2,840.70   Snowbird Couple: $4,096.63
November Promotion Price:  Snowbird Single: $2,434.88   Snowbird Couple: $3,511.40
Notes:
$1,500 Initiation Fee is Waived
Prices do not include the 7.5% Florida sales tax.
Prices do not include the Membership Certificate Fee:  Single: $250   Couple: $500
Snowbird Members must provide proof of both Florida and out-state-state residences.
Partial months are pro-rated.
2025 Trial Membership Promotion
Join January 1, 2025 through September 30, 2025
Buy a Trial membership of 3 months or more and get 1 additional month FREE!
Not valid with any other membership program. Must be a new first-time member.

Golf and Social Events
Come for the Golf, Stay for the Friends!
Golf Events
Sunday 18-hole golf mixer played on the 2nd Sunday every month
Friday 9-hole twilight golf mixer played every Friday
Social Events
Caloosa Casual Party Club
Parties are held on the first Monday of February, March, April, May, October, November and December.
BYOB, Buffet dinners, Music and Dancing.
Upon arrival, table numbers are drawn for table assignments, offering the opportunity to meet new members.
Other Events During the Year
Patrick’s Day Party
Fourth of July Party
Halloween Party
New Year’s Eve Party
Las Vegas Show Parties
Book Club
Card Club
Caloosa has a great banquet space for your next event. Great for wedding receptions, awards banquets, birthday or other special parties. The banquet room seats up to 200 people, has a dance floor, large screen projector, microphones plus catering and entertainment contacts to help you plan your special event.

About
Come for the Golf, Stay for the Friends!
Caloosa Golf & Country Club is located in Sun City Center, a premier active adult community in the Tampa Bay area.
A private member-owned golf club that welcomes golfers of all skill levels and has many social activities.
One of the best maintained courses in the area
Explore our website and learn why Caloosa Golf & Country Club should be your next destination
Evening dinner/dance parties – catered lunches and dinners
Bridge Club
Karaoke
Golf scrambles every Friday and once a month on Sunday
Combined golf and social events celebrating Memorial Day, Independence Day and more, many followed by a catered meal
Member-held private parties and receptions
Combined golf and social events.
Las Vegas Show parties
Halloween Parties
